Staria has long, dark hair (worn long in the back and braided in the
front) and large, dark, liquid brown eyes.  She is of average height
and weight, but has been told by some that she is quite buxom.  Staria
dresses in the long, dark dress and voluminous robes of a peasant.
A dagger is at her side at all times.  Staria is her stallion husband
Pooka's pride and joy.

